org.mxupdate.mapping
Class Mapping_mxJPO

java.lang.Object
  org.mxupdate.mapping.Mapping_mxJPO

public class Mapping_mxJPO
extends Object

The class is used to map from used names within the MxUpdate JPOs and the internal used names within MX.
